{"tid":951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"討論區新時代，林祖舜不敵腦燒祝福～","createTime":"2016-11-25T15:34:41.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-25T16:18:47.000Z","uid":5189,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ea9aee8c245cfc3a88a7a4ba829cbd9cc0a4f8c2","tid":951,"uid":5189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T15:34:41.000Z","msg":"我只能夠講，討論區又進入一個新時代；由Smartphone主導既新時代。<br />\n由於高登林祖舜不思進取、故步自封，成就左新論點既誕生。就好似過往BBS、Newsgroup一樣，隨住科技既進步加上自身既局限而沒落。<br />\n<br />\n討論區已經由網頁版面進化成App介面主導，足以印證Steve Jobs講過桌面電腦走下坡呢個預言。<br />\n<br />\n無一樣野可以阻擋科技潮流，林祖舜當然唔例外，當年燈神腦豪情壯語講用2000萬買起既高登，亦難敵燈神既「祝福」而變得一文不值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d1661d515f7b5f89d808fb8d046b99cdce0c665","tid":951,"uid":2638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T15:35:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2ee176e63e8619c33af76770ecafd9c1a0c75b1","tid":951,"uid":5189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T15:54:03.000Z","msg":"推下先～"},{"pid":"b509eb6dd8a0f70c58e664e614b1ec38f60f5ca9","tid":951,"uid":281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T15:55:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bab1c19cfd81151262f610938297b72ca0153505","tid":951,"uid":8301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T16:00:05.000Z","msg":"皇天擊殺林早洩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f2ac4ec04cea9aa03f830d5b11fb5237e1c2470","tid":951,"uid":9460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T16:02:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class